---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fernando Delgado - Product Leader | 5x Founder | Former Google, YouTube, Yahoo" bodyClass="collection-type-page homepage">

  <!-- Full-width banner photo at 50% aspect ratio (original image: 7740x3870) -->
  <div class="sqs-block image-block">
    <div class="image-block-outer-wrapper">
      <figure class="sqs-block-image-figure intrinsic">
        <div class="image-block-wrapper">
          <div style="height:350px;overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;">
            <img
              src="/images/fernando-delgado.jpg"
              alt=""
              loading="eager"
              width="7740"
              height="3870"
              style="display:block;object-fit:cover;width:100%;height:100%;object-position:50% 50%;"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <figcaption class="image-caption-wrapper">
          <div class="image-caption"><p>Fernando Delgado - Product Executive  | 5x Founder | Ex-Google, YouTube, Yahoo | Lifelong Learner</p></div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bio text -->
  <div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html">
    <div class="sqs-block-content">
      <div class="sqs-html-content">
        <p>Fernando Delgado builds products that blend purpose, simplicity, and global scale. With two decades of experience launching and growing industry-defining platforms, he brings a rare mix of entrepreneurial drive and corporate leadership expertise.</p>

        <p>Fernando is a seasoned product leader and 5x founder with a track record of building and scaling technology that impacts billions. Over the past 16+ years, he's led high-impact teams at Google, YouTube, and Yahoo, shipping products used daily around the globe.</p>

        <p>At Google, Fernando co-led the development of Backup by Google One, now integrated into more than 2 billion Android devices. This effort allowed Google to scale its mobile storage business from $50M to over $1B ARR through deep integrations and partnerships with Photos, Gmail, Drive, and Android. At YouTube, he shaped the strategy for YouTube Courses, a structured learning product designed to support creator-led education.</p>

        <p>Fernando's entrepreneurial work is just as notable. He's founded 5 ventures, each focused on unlocking human potential through thoughtful technology and design. Most recently, he co-founded Techito, which quickly became Colorado's top-rated short-term rental brand, powered by automation, AI workflows, and operational precision.</p>

        <p>Based in Barcelona, Fernando blends Silicon Valley product rigor with a founder's adaptability and vision. He is actively exploring senior product leadership opportunities where he can help ambitious teams tackle complex challenges and deliver meaningful outcomes.</p>

        <p>If you're interested in getting in touch, please send a note to <a href="mailto:hello@fernandodelgado.com" target="_blank"><strong>hello@fernandodelgado.com</strong></a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
